claim.claim-text:
A method for manufacturing a solar cell module having a plurality of solar cells arranged between a surface protecting member and backing film,

the method including a step of arranging in parallel a plurality of solar cell strings including a plurality of electrically connected solar cells, and electrically connecting the wiring members positioned at the end portions of adjacent strings using transition wiring;

at least one end portion of the transition wiring being bent, and the bent portion oriented towards the surface protecting member and connected to the wiring member.
